  </tr></table>Hey guys.<br><br>I have recently moved to the Stormhammer(Legends) server. I did it this past Sunday. Don't worry, for those of you who may care( :-p ), I WILL be back by June 11th on my next billing cycle.<br>I just went to Stormhammer to have a better chance to get to know lvling/raiding spots in zones that I would otherwise not have too much access at on our server.<br><br>I do have some suggestions to help out the guild:<br>Verant has done us a HUGE favor by making the Planes of Power Expansion.<br>For those of us, lvl 53+, there is NO better experience than a good, well rounded exp group in the Planes.<br><br>For those of you who are 46-52, I would suggest you guys regularly do Plane of Justice groups by the zoneline. There is Great EXP There. Another good spot in PoJ is in the basement. If anyone wants me to lead them to these spots post it on this board and I'll show you on a mule I have on Tallon.<br><br>For those of you 53+, I have found that a well rounded group that includes at LEAST a upper 50s Tank, an upper 50s healer, and a 58+ enchanter/Shaman will give you GREAT exp in PoD by the Left side of the Castle. You can also do smaller exp groups by kyting in PoN. <br>There are GREAT places to EXP in PoP. Don't be afraid of the other PK guilds. Just find a little niche and level up. Hopefully, by this time next month, we'll all be in our upper 50s, low 60s. :-)
